---
layout: haiku
title: Baby Caterpillar
author: wdhenarangoda
---

I am but a caterpillar </br>
surrounded by butterflies </br>
such beautiful creatures </br>
i have watched many like me change </br>
change with such grace into such beauty </br>
i often wonder why </br> 
why i am yet to find such grace </br>
why am i yet to change into such beauty </br>
